{"tid":997462,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加評論員出書剖析中國滲透　指加國領導持續誤判使中共受益","createTime":"2019-01-27T07:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T10:27:16.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"75592f6de3a0d9a91e2119310eb4dec9f3b4edaa","tid":997462,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T07:52:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/27/155212_b5f849e67f991eaf4d308e5bf3aaf5d6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F27%2F155212_b5f849e67f991eaf4d308e5bf3aaf5d6.png&h=a9a13498&s={SIZE}\" />中加關係隨著華為副董事長兼財務總監孟晚舟被捕而持續升溫，加拿大國際事務專欄作家文達峰（Jonathan Manthorpe）本月初出版新書《Claws of the Panda: Beijing&rsquo;s Campaign of Influence and Intimidation in Canada》，剖析北京多年來在加國的滲透行動。<br />\n<br />\n根據作品簡介，該作談及加拿大未能認清與對抗，中國共產黨在商界、政界、學術界與傳媒方面的滲透及影響，以及對加拿大人的控制。書中詳細描述近150年來加中關係的演變，加拿大領導如何持續誤判，令中共及其代理人因為加拿大的天真而從中受益。<br />\n<br />\n文達峰在書中指出，加拿大人對中國有良性的理解，使得他們容易成為中國政權的目標。由加拿大與中華民國斷交、改於中國建交開始，中國政府就開始在當地建立經濟、政治以及人際關係網絡。雖然建立這些關係通常是合法的，但由中共組織的行動，卻是透過國家機關、間諜、線人等進行，例如以「統一戰線」控制所有海外華人「友好協會」。<br />\n<br />\n（圖片來源：Jonathan Manthorpe twitter、<a href=\"http://amazon.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Famazon.com&d=LfVst80bDa3Z%2FR5Vf3xtfjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=1a7079a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">amazon.com</a>）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/268317/加評論員出書剖析中國滲透%E3%80%80指加國領導持續誤判/?fbclid=IwAR17Dj8GAS8VUsk_HQ2N2A_pmOZjPDjZ9L2J7CQ3lj3jgK0BPKeuiIjokg4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F268317%2F%E5%8A%A0%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96%E5%93%A1%E5%87%BA%E6%9B%B8%E5%89%96%E6%9E%90%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%BB%B2%E9%80%8F%25E3%2580%2580%E6%8C%87%E5%8A%A0%E5%9C%8B%E9%A0%98%E5%B0%8E%E6%8C%81%E7%BA%8C%E8%AA%A4%E5%88%A4%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR17Dj8GAS8VUsk_HQ2N2A_pmOZjPDjZ9L2J7CQ3lj3jgK0BPKeuiIjokg4&d=LfVst80bDa3Z%2FR5Vf3xtfjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=af38733c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/268317/加評論員出書剖析中國滲透%E3%80%80指加國領導持續誤判/?fbclid=IwAR17Dj8GAS8VUsk_HQ2N2A_pmOZjPDjZ9L2J7CQ3lj3jgK0BPKeuiIjokg4</a>"},{"pid":"ce206e8d6dbb51137777f2df77c0accaaf4810d4","tid":997462,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T08:04:13.000Z","msg":"有冇中文版"},{"pid":"4db7d8c063ea8dc96108291b3c407c2eb7f47622","tid":997462,"uid":36143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T10:27:16.000Z","msg":"lm"}]}